  "prompt": "Is there any management quota at PCCOE Pune? What are the fees?",
  "response": "As of my last update in October 2023, the Pimpri Chinchwad College of Engineering (PCCOE) in Pune does have a management quota for admissions. The management quota allows students to secure a seat without going through the regular entrance exam process, though it usually involves higher fees compared to the general quota.\n\nThe specific fees for the management quota can vary from year to year and may also differ depending on the course of study. It's best to check the official PCCOE website or contact their admissions office directly for the most accurate and up-to-date information regarding fees, eligibility, and the management quota process.\n\nIf you need further details, visiting the official site or reaching out to the institution directly would be the best course of action.",
